ConditionPatientGivenNameSearchParameter

Parameter patient.given:string

Searches for condition based on the patient's given name(s) eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Condition?patient.given={givenName}

ResourceCondition
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesCondition
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
